title: 1960–61 National Football League (Ireland)
text:
The 1960–61 National Football League was the 30th staging of the <a href="National%20Football%20League%20%28Ireland%29">National Football League</a> (NFL), an annual <a href="Gaelic%20football">Gaelic football</a> tournament for the <a href="Gaelic%20Athletic%20Association%20county">Gaelic Athletic Association county</a> teams of <a href="Ireland">Ireland</a>.
Kerry won the final by 20 points.
